title: Shaun Micallef's Mad As Hell
description:
This is an almost complete collection of Shaun Micallef's Mad As Hell (Series 01-04) from the Australian Broadcasting Corporation (ABC TV). It's political satire at its best, has some classic characters and is a complete 'up yours' to conventional news presenting. It has made me laugh and I hope it goes down well on the Pirate Bay.

The quality varies as it is from different sources, but it's all good.

Cheers,
MoofieMan.

PS: If this torrent works OK, I'd like to upload some cool moofies with remastered soundtracks (so that you can hear the bloody dialogue for a change)
